text: Livia Zaugg (born 29 January 1996, Kilchberg, Zürich) is a Swiss volleyball player. She is a member of the Women's National Team. She participated at the 2018 Montreux Volley Masters. She plays for Sm'Aesch Pfeffingen. == References == == External links == * FIVB Profile * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss women's volleyball players Category:People from Horgen District
